  >- asm_simp_tac bool_ss []
  \\ rpt strip_tac
  \\ `x + y <= x + z` by metis_tac[REAL_LE_LADD_IMP]
  \\ `x + z = x + y` by metis_tac[REAL_LE_ANTISYM]
  \\ `~x + x + z = ~x + x + y` by metis_tac[REAL_ADD_ASSOC]
  \\ `z = y` by metis_tac[REAL_ADD_LID,REAL_ADD_LINV]
